---
import Layout from '../layouts/BlogPost.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="About"
	description="About AI Tools Hub"
	pubDate={new Date('November 11 2025')}
>
	<style>
		/* Dark mode styles */
		:global(body) {
			background: #0a0a0a;
			color: #e0e0e0;
		}

		article {
			max-width: 800px;
			margin: 0 auto;
			padding: 2rem;
			line-height: 1.8;
		}

		h1, h2, h3 {
			color: #ffffff;
			font-weight: 600;
		}

		h1 {
			font-size: 2.5rem;
			margin-bottom: 2rem;
			background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
			-webkit-background-clip: text;
			-webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
			background-clip: text;
		}

		h2 {
			font-size: 1.8rem;
			margin-top: 2.5rem;
			margin-bottom: 1rem;
			color: #667eea;
		}

		p {
			color: #b0b0b0;
			margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
			font-size: 1.1rem;
		}

		strong {
			color: #ffffff;
			font-weight: 600;
		}

		ul {
			list-style: none;
			padding: 0;
			margin: 1.5rem 0;
		}

		li {
			padding-left: 1.5rem;
			margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
			position: relative;
			color: #b0b0b0;
		}

		li::before {
			content: "â†’";
			position: absolute;
			left: 0;
			color: #667eea;
			font-weight: bold;
		}

		.highlight {
			background: rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.1);
			border-left: 3px solid #667eea;
			padding: 1.5rem;
			border-radius: 8px;
			margin: 2rem 0;
		}

		.highlight p {
			margin-bottom: 0;
		}
	</style>

	<article>
		<h1>About AI Tools Hub</h1>
		
		<p>
			<strong>AI Tools Hub</strong> is your trusted resource for finding the best AI-powered software solutions. 
			We test, compare, and review AI tools so you can make informed decisions without wasting time or money.
		</p>

		<h2>What We Do</h2>
		<p>
			We publish <strong>in-depth, data-driven reviews</strong> of AI writing tools, productivity software, 
			and SaaS solutions. Our content is designed to help:
		</p>
		<ul>
			<li><strong>Content creators</strong> scale their output without sacrificing quality</li>
			<li><strong>Businesses</strong> find affordable alternatives to expensive tools</li>
			<li><strong>Startups</strong> leverage AI to compete with bigger companies</li>
			<li><strong>Individuals</strong> discover tools that save time and boost productivity</li>
		</ul>

		<h2>Why Trust Us?</h2>
		<div class="highlight">
			<p>
				<strong>Real testing, real data.</strong> We don't just regurgitate marketing copy. 
				Every tool we review is tested with real workflows, measured for performance, 
				and analyzed for cost-effectiveness.
			</p>
		</div>

		<h2>Our Review Process</h2>
		<ul>
			<li>Hands-on testing with real use cases</li>
			<li>Performance benchmarks and time-to-value analysis</li>
			<li>Cost comparison across similar tools</li>
			<li>Honest pros & cons (we highlight limitations)</li>
			<li>Regular updates as tools evolve</li>
		</ul>

		<h2>Who We Help</h2>
		<p>
			Whether you're a solo creator, growing startup, or established business, 
			our guides help you choose the right AI tools for your specific needs and budget.
		</p>

		<p>
			<strong>Questions or suggestions?</strong> Reach us at: 
			<a href="mailto:contact@ai-tools-hub.com" style="color: #667eea; text-decoration: none;">
				contact@ai-tools-hub.com
			</a>
		</p>
	</article>
</Layout>
